        <Parent_String>Native South Andean styles [300017933], Native Andean [300017918], Native South American [300017879], Native American [300017437], The Americas [300016617], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
